org.lemming.data

Class GenericFrame<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lemming.data.GenericFrame<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - - data type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, Frame<T>

    public class GenericFrame<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Frame<T>
    A GenericFrame is an implementation of Frame which includes basic fields like width, height and frame number. It provides a template for a basic Frame.
    Author:
    Thomas Pengo, Joe Borbely
